%package sybase
Summary: Sybase ODBC connectivity module for Meta-HTML.
Group: Applications/WWW
Requires: metahtml

%description sybaseodbc
Using modsybaseodbc.so, you can enable the connection of Meta-HTML to a
Sybase Anywhere Server by soft linking /usr/lib/libsybase.so to
/opt/SYBSasa6/lib/dbodbc6.so (the Sybase ODBC drivers).

%files sybase
/usr/lib/metahtml/modsybaseodbc.so

